title: ADC looking for SCU team
body:
Hi Guys

ADC here looking for a team with Southern Cross Uni. Hit me up!

replies.body: Would be down to start a team if you guys are keen
Hey man, im also looking for a team with SCU, found anything yet?
No, haven't found anyone yet. Which SCU campus are you from?
The Hotel School in Sydney, we are run by SCU though.
